{
  "texts": [
    "Jurgens et al. [2017] use location-based filters available on Twitter at the time.",
    "They use language identification classifiers to predict the language and identify dialectal users.",
    "Husain et al. [2022] obtain tweets from Kuwait to create a dataset of tweets in the Kuwaiti dialect of Arabic.",
    "Coats [2022] create an unlabeled dataset of Youtube comments.",
    "They start with a list of councils in Australia, extract official Youtube channels and retrieve comments."
  ]
}